{
  "doc_id": "37026",
  "text": "Two additional study visits at day 60 after implant injection were performed to measure the IOP. Management of postoperative elevated IOP followed an algorithm previously approved by an independent glaucoma specialist who was a member of the external DMC. [CITATION_1] Any additional vitreoretinal surgical interventions over the trial period were considered reoperations and recorded as such. Indirect laser retinopexy was performed at the discretion of the patient's vitreoretinal consultant and was not considered a reoperation.",
